<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>RRR Universe</title>

<style>
*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:Arial, sans-serif;
scroll-behavior:smooth;
}

body{
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#000000,#0f172a,#111827);
color:white;
}

header{
display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
align-items:center;
padding:20px 8%;
background:rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
position:sticky;
top:0;
}

.logo{
font-size:28px;
font-weight:bold;
color:#FFD700;
}

nav a{
color:white;
text-decoration:none;
margin-left:20px;
}

.hero{
height:100vh;
display:flex;
flex-direction:column;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
text-align:center;
padding:20px;
}

.hero h1{
font-size:60px;
color:#FFD700;
margin-bottom:15px;
}

.hero p{
max-width:700px;
font-size:18px;
line-height:1.8;
}

.btn{
display:inline-block;
margin-top:25px;
padding:14px 30px;
background:#FFD700;
color:black;
text-decoration:none;
font-weight:bold;
border-radius:30px;
}

section{
padding:80px 10%;
}

h2{
text-align:center;
color:#FFD700;
margin-bottom:30px;
}

.about{
text-align:center;
max-width:800px;
margin:auto;
line-height:1.8;
}

.cards{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
gap:20px;
}

.card{
background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
padding:25px;
border-radius:15px;
backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
}

.contact{
text-align:center;
}

footer{
text-align:center;
padding:20px;
background:black;
margin-top:50px;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
<div class="logo">RRR Universe</div>

<nav>
<a href="#home">Home</a>
<a href="#about">About</a>
<a href="#mission">Mission</a>
<a href="#contact">Contact</a>
</nav>
</header>

<section class="hero" id="home">

<h1>RRR Universe</h1>

<p>
Learn • Trade • Grow Together
</p>

<p style="margin-top:15px;">
A community built for new traders who want to learn,
connect, share ideas and grow together in the financial markets.
</p>

<a class="btn"
href="https://instagram.com/rrr_universe_"
target="_blank">
Join Community
</a>

</section>

<section id="about">

<h2>About Us</h2>

<div class="about">

<p>
RRR Universe is a growing community created to connect new traders.
Our goal is to help beginners learn trading, share knowledge,
exchange ideas and build confidence together.
</p>

</div>

</section>

<section id="mission">

<h2>Our Mission</h2>

<div class="cards">

<div class="card">
<h3>Learn</h3>
<p>Understand trading fundamentals and market psychology.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Connect</h3>
<p>Meet like-minded traders and share experiences.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Grow</h3>
<p>Improve skills through continuous learning and discipline.</p>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<section id="contact">

<h2>Join Our Community</h2>

<div class="contact">

<p>Instagram: @rrr_universe_</p>

<br>

<a class="btn"
href="https://instagram.com/rrr_universe_"
target="_blank">
Follow on Instagram
</a>

</div>

</section>

<footer>
© 2026 RRR Universe | Trading Community
</footer>

</body>
</html>